## Manual Operations — AI Must Guide Founder

Founder does hands-on tasks; AI provides **step-by-step** instructions until complete.

**Always guide end-to-end when asked:**
- Supabase: SQL run, RLS, storage buckets, edge function deploy
- `.env`: which file, which key, where to paste from dashboard
- Backend: FastAPI deploy, env vars, CORS, webhook URLs
- Payments: Razorpay/Stripe webhook setup
- Android/iOS build & store (iOS App Store only when founder ready — ~3 months)

**Format:** numbered steps, exact paths, copy-paste commands, "verify" checkpoint after each step.

Do not say "configure Supabase" without showing how.

